:55:20.000Z","msg":"老麥隔離？<br />\n<br />\n呢個位星期一至日都旺到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朝早到夜晚都超多人流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係荃灣最旺ge位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22aa1118b97f5d938059b003792b1da98e166021","tid":248080,"uid":32393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T00:58:23.000Z","msg":"唔記得邊到聽返嚟，間鋪嘅上一手老細為咗呃保險金，放火燒自己間鋪，點知燒死咗自己個老婆，之後就再冇人租"},{"pid":"f417fae6022508a8034cfa4207c57458b7ebd7d6","tid":248080,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T01:06:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔記得邊到聽返嚟，間鋪嘅上一手老細為咗呃保險金，放火燒自己間鋪，點知燒死咗自己個老婆，之後就再冇人租</blockquote><br />\n嘩想聽詳細資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128dd53db803008744b9c3d223d54568264eeb15","tid":248080,"uid":9347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T01:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似有故仔，風水野黎。<br />\n<br />\n唔講，驚自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔講死全家</blockquote><br />\n咩都風水，收皮啦，怪力亂神<br />\n實情係物業估價同租金直接掛鉤，減你一兩千知唔知會對個估價有幾大影響？<br />\n估價低左仲點同銀行借錢。<br />\n利伸，跟緊師傅學做private banking <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f094c63c1ee762f7d64719c1fe57f144fd71581","tid":248080,"uid":648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T01:41:25.000Z","msg":"以前係佐記？ 定隔離？"},{"pid":"75f7f7eb1af5027b6566fca18108334067e0e3ea","tid":248080,"uid":47491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T01:45:46.000Z","msg":"聽聞入面好猛"},{"pid":"b4a1ec71afd32f6f9b935ab147140dacedbc8fcf","tid":248080,"uid":2884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T01:49:36.000Z","msg":"呢個鋪位好撚猛㗎"},{"pid":"b7c2fec146b1086b368568933e887afc31f8c954","tid":248080,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T01:51:01.000Z","msg":"好多草猛"},{"pid":"d5f8890f5aa9aa866155c0f4e118991af472984f","tid":248080,"uid":40303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T01:53:51.000Z","msg":"以前細個記得好似係CSL(定隔離鋪位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n之後執左就無再見過其他鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e71904cf6fe8ed6b38b6dacb17dc2a947cadd3","tid":248080,"uid":8122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T01:54:38.000Z","msg":"以前好似係金鋪黎"},{"pid":"358a742f3908c4d8b323dce5d6b310b3867f5ddc","tid":248080,"uid":61920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T01:57:35.000Z","msg":"有日凌晨行過聽到入面有人聲<br />\n仲要係大叫果啲聲<br />\n果陣攰得濟唔為意<br />\n無理到"},{"pid":"7ea5a495d53a2133caed7b0e953843bfc8887cca","tid":248080,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T01:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/173708_7265e0ec68aeafaaf7b980d1c54eb3fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F173708_7265e0ec68aeafaaf7b980d1c54eb3fa.jpg&h=fa4af802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實目測已五六年了，角位大單邊，係咪天價！<br />\n呢啲業主真係好勁，可以忍咁耐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢棟樓店舖業主都癲癲地架, 我懷疑係同一人, 出價離晒地<br />\n棟樓對住街市, 之前俾名創垃圾店租左既位置, 而定放售1億, 痴燃線既, 邊值呢個價, 一世都賣唔出啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又話貪字得個貧，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜事實係越有錢越貪！<br />\n而且係越貪越有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n這就是香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7801f5a5acfb839712a0f1a3124e183d98dce9","tid":248080,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:01:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似有故仔，風水野黎。<br />\n<br />\n唔講，驚自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔講死全家</blockquote><br />\n咩都風水，收皮啦，怪力亂神<br />\n實情係物業估價同租金直接掛鉤，減你一兩千知唔知會對個估價有幾大影響？<br />\n估價低左仲點同銀行借錢。<br />\n利伸，跟緊師傅學做private banking <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n風水唔關事，我明，但可以做散貨場短租都大把人要，一個月都收番十萬啦，五年有成600萬吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇AA解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dba5092d94f66e9f4f0299bf5ee0ceae5d02441","tid":248080,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似有故仔，風水野黎。<br />\n<br />\n唔講，驚自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔講死全家</blockquote><br />\n咩都風水，收皮啦，怪力亂神<br />\n實情係物業估價同租金直接掛鉤，減你一兩千知唔知會對個估價有幾大影響？<br />\n估價低左仲點同銀行借錢。<br />\n利伸，跟緊師傅學做private banking <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n風水唔關事，我明，但可以做散貨場短租都大把人要，一個月都收番十萬啦，五年有成600萬吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇AA解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買得呢啲地鋪都唔志在嗰十萬八萬一個月，貪嗰少少令銀行批少千幾二千萬俾你？<br />\n依家出面啲租金都係煲出嚟，係個業主唔識玩先會空咁耐。幫過一個客做過一單係原價三萬租，嗌七萬搵熟人租，每個月私底下過返四萬俾個朋友。"},{"pid":"aa811284d84b6c634b31272ca529df0fc436db3a","tid":248080,"uid":9594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:37:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/173708_7265e0ec68aeafaaf7b980d1c54eb3fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F173708_7265e0ec68aeafaaf7b980d1c54eb3fa.jpg&h=fa4af802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實目測已五六年了，角位大單邊，係咪天價！<br />\n呢啲業主真係好勁，可以忍咁耐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢棟樓店舖業主都癲癲地架, 我懷疑係同一人, 出價離晒地<br />\n棟樓對住街市, 之前俾名創垃圾店租左既位置, 而定放售1億, 痴燃線既, 邊值呢個價, 一世都賣唔出啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以香港黎講 話唔定真係會有一日會值一億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd21291c45bf4e13b02ede065c6995bc922b567","tid":248080,"uid":32393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔記得邊到聽返嚟，間鋪嘅上一手老細為咗呃保險金，放火燒自己間鋪，點知燒死咗自己個老婆，之後就再冇人租</blockquote><br />\n嘩想聽詳細資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廿幾定三十幾年前，嗰間舖好似係賣衫嘅，但個老細爭人錢，就諗咗條屎橋岀嚟，諗住燒咗間鋪去呃保險金，跟住佢老婆起閣樓唔知點解走唔到被火燒死咗。之後聽講嗰個單位成日見到佢老婆飄嚟飄去，跟住就冇人再租喇<br />\n利申:聽老一輩講，住咗荃灣五十幾年"},{"pid":"5373f0a758b28ac244a5ca2c9cde6beee2fffa31","tid":248080,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔記得邊到聽返嚟，間鋪嘅上一手老細為咗呃保險金，放火燒自己間鋪，點知燒死咗自己個老婆，之後就再冇人租</blockquote><br />\n嘩想聽詳細資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廿幾定三十幾年前，嗰間舖好似係賣衫嘅，但個老細爭人錢，就諗咗條